App have 2 features selling and buying.
Buying feature-
if(buying == true){
  if(user.hasAmount >= crypto.price){
    company.crypto.quantity = company.crypto.quantity-1
    user.crypto.quantity = user.crypto.quantity + 1
    user.hasAmount == user.hasAmount- crypto.price
    company.hasAmount = company.hasAmount+crypto.price
    }
    else{
    print("user has not enough money")
    }
 }
 else{
 print("user don't want to buy")
}
